Little_Rock.Vanetten House: The Vanetten House is a historic house at 1012 Cumberland Street in Little Rock, Arkansas. It is a two-story wood frame American Foursquare house, with a dormered hip roof, weatherboard siding, and brick foundation. The roof and dormers have extended eaves with exposed rafters, and a single-story porch wraps across the front and around one side, supported by Ionic columns.
